-- In English Gestoria - Remote-friendly tax and accounting services for expats nationwide
('In English Gestoria', 'Tax/Accounting', 'Remote-friendly, English-speaking gestoría (tax and accounting firm) based in Spain serving expats, freelancers, digital nomads and international clients nationwide. Founded by Servando Rodríguez (former KPMG tax consultant) and Karelys Ospino (former KPMG audit consultant and Head of Accounting for McDonald''s largest franchisee), with over 10 years of experience each. The team brings expertise from Big Four consulting firms combined with modern digital workflows and ERP implementation. Core services include bookkeeping, quarterly and annual tax filings, payroll and Social Security management, business structure and tax planning, and regulatory compliance. Specializes in international tax optimization, assisting clients with tax residency transitions to Spain, and finding optimal legal structures (freelancer, self-employed, or company) for tax efficiency. Fully remote-capable with centralized, real-time access to financial and tax information. Serves clients across Spain from Tenerife to Madrid with clear, professional communication in English. Offers free orientation calls and transparent digital processes.', 'Av. Hermando Fernández Perdigón, 6, Piso 7, Apto. 718', 'Puerto de la Cruz', 'Santa Cruz de Tenerife', '+34 642 723 277', 'hola@inenglishgestoria.es', 'https://www.inenglishgestoria.es/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
